---
<section class="bg-stone-50 py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="container max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">What's inside?</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Every ingredient is visible in the jar. No powders, no fillers — just nature's perfect hydration formula.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Real Fruit -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-4xl">🍋</div>
        <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium">Real Fruit</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Freeze-dried, organic. Natural glucose for real cellular absorption.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- French Gray Sea Salt -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-4xl">🌊</div>
        <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium">Sea Salt</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">French gray sea salt. 60+ trace minerals. Sodium, potassium, magnesium & more.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Nothing else -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-4xl">✦</div>
        <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium">Nothing Else</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Zero sugar. Zero maltodextrin. Zero artificial anything. Ever.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Visible ingredients -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-4xl">👁</div>
        <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium">See It</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Every ingredient is visible in your jar. If you can't see it, it's not there.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/products" class="mt-10 inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-foreground px-8 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors">
      Shop all flavors →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
